name: Polo Collar Cotton T-shirt
description: Off White T-shirt for men Solid Regular length Polo collar Short, regular sleeves Knitted cotton fabric With Nova, the traditional Polo makes a stylish comeback. We took the breathable and utterly smooth 100% super combed fabric that has a natural, luxe feel to create our t-shirts. We also went ahead and added ribbed cuffs for a snug fit. The cotton pique fabric adds an element of textural play, while the ribbed collar coupled with the two-button placket gives a smart sign-off to this classic silhouette. Shaped to a regular fit, these tagless designs are ideal for an effortless day-to-night look.  Key Features :-  Ultra-soft - Our Nova collection is made from super combed cotton that's breathable and utterly smooth at the same time. It feels super-soft and gentle against the skin.  Ultra-breathable - The super combed cotton fabric is moisture absorbing for a breathable feel all day.  IntelliEaze - It's enhanced with IntelliEaze technology for the most luxurious comfort that guarantees unmatched lightness, softness and breathability.  Classic silhouette -The cotton pique fabric adds an element of textural play, while the ribbed collar coupled with the two-button placket gives a smart sign-off to this classic silhouette.  Day to night - With Nova, the traditional polo makes a stylish comeback making it ideal for an effortless day to night look.

name: Men Slim Fit Formal Trousers
description: About The Product: Introducing The Pant Project Stretchable Pants for Men -- the perfect blend of comfort, style, and versatility. Say goodbye to wrinkles and discomfort with these expertly designed pants. Featuring advanced stretch technology, they move with you, ensuring you always look sharp and polished, no matter where the day takes you. Crafted from a unique blend of lightweight, moisture-wicking fabric, these pants keep you cool and dry even during the hottest days, making them the perfect choice for all-day wear. From boardrooms to casual outings, you'll stay stylish and comfortable with every step.  Fabric Quality: Made with the finest export-quality materials, these smart-casual pants are a testament to superior craftsmanship. The fabric is a carefully balanced mix of 62% Polyester, 34% Viscose & 4% Elastane, offering not only supreme comfort but also durability and flexibility. Whether you're traveling, at work, or just on the go, these pants deliver unmatched ease of movement and long-lasting wear.  Slim Fit: Designed for the modern man, the slim-fit cut hugs from waist to ankle, giving a streamlined silhouette without sacrificing comfort. It's the ideal choice for those who want to strike a balance between casual ease and polished, semi-formal attire.  Style Tip: Elevate your look effortlessly by pairing these pants with a crisp button-down shirt for a more formal appeal, or go for a laid-back vibe by teaming them with a polo or t-shirt. The options are endless, making them a wardrobe essential.  Occasion: Versatile and stylish, these pants can seamlessly transition from day to night. Wear them to an important office meeting with a sharp white shirt or dress them up with a tux for your best friend's wedding.

name: Men Slim Fit Formal Trousers
description: About The Product: Introducing The Pant Project Stretchable Pants for Men -- the perfect blend of comfort, style, and versatility. Say goodbye to wrinkles and discomfort with these expertly designed pants. Featuring advanced stretch technology, they move with you, ensuring you always look sharp and polished, no matter where the day takes you. Crafted from a unique blend of lightweight, moisture-wicking fabric, these pants keep you cool and dry even during the hottest days, making them the perfect choice for all-day wear. From boardrooms to casual outings, you'll stay stylish and comfortable with every step.  Fabric Quality: Made with the finest export-quality materials, these smart-casual pants are a testament to superior craftsmanship. The fabric is a carefully balanced mix of 62% Polyester, 34% Viscose & 4% Elastane, offering not only supreme comfort but also durability and flexibility. Whether you're traveling, at work, or just on the go, these pants deliver unmatched ease of movement and long-lasting wear.  Slim Fit: Designed for the modern man, the slim-fit cut hugs from waist to ankle, giving a streamlined silhouette without sacrificing comfort. It's the ideal choice for those who want to strike a balance between casual ease and polished, semi-formal attire.  Style Tip: Elevate your look effortlessly by pairing these pants with a crisp button-down shirt for a more formal appeal, or go for a laid-back vibe by teaming them with a polo or t-shirt. The options are endless, making them a wardrobe essential.  Occasion: Versatile and stylish, these pants can seamlessly transition from day to night. Wear them to an important office meeting with a sharp white shirt or dress them up with a tux for your best friend's wedding.

Motifs are transferred onto light coloured background with wooden blocks following two techniques - direct and resist. Bagru motifs are mostly derived from the flora and fauna and are natural in origin.  Product Details:  Beige & black printed kurta Indie printed A-line shape High Slit Round neck, sleeveless Knee length with straight hem Pure cotton machine weave fabric Disclaimer: This is a handcrafted kurta, and is prone to colour bleeding due to use of natural dyes The print on the garment might be uneven owning to the handcrafted nature of the product, adding essence to the garment. Taavi uses sustainable thread for the manufacturing of its garments.
